17-09-06T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fe36b7a4b1310ffacc6ad601cd753137ffe2d2e","tid":389093,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"同妹妹一間房 個衰妹成日唔著衫訓覺 要我幫佢cum被"},{"pid":"ee2f518ee03b6a627888c05d39f8fa194ea4062a","tid":389093,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"同細佬同房 相差五年<br />\n細個覺得佢係黎瓜分我既愛<br />\n成日怪屋企人做咩生佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家就還好啦<br />\n係單人床冇咁好訓啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7878306af8561cec2b1c06fbfcbf25105135f5","tid":389093,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29e052f36c6a4277bed689fe6387eaf324cbdd14","tid":389093,"uid":139238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"同細我三年嘅細佬一間房，關係好好<br />\n有時星期六日同放假傾計傾到三四點先訓，乜都講一餐<br />\n<br />\n一個成熟爆登嘅細佬，而我就係個個傻傻地不懂世事嘅家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b503f43b15dd8236a1a6f3f619d77918c4434ccd","tid":389093,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"妹 同房"}]}